wikipedia_page.main: Joshua Ian Ron Cooke (born 4 February 1997) is an English footballer who plays for Southern League Premier Central side Stratford Town, where he plays as a forward.

response: In 2006, he starred in Four Kings, and Big Day, neither of which was renewed. He appeared in Curb Your Enthusiasm."What Are They Up To? Big Day's Josh Cooke", buddytv.com; accessed April 7, 2016. In 2009, Cooke appeared in the Joss Whedon show Dollhouse as Leo Carpenter.
